So when it comes to current events (both the obvious ones, and ones that may come to be known in the future) I have two prime directives.

The first is that my core goal can and must be to destroy capitalism. Chancers are if you are following me at this point that's not something one would object to.

The second is, I oppose the oppressor whomever it is, always.

Whether it's the conflict in Israel/Palestine, the construction of Cop City, the ongoing trans genocide in the Imperial core, the calls for Landback and decolonization, or any other number of things; I will always oppose the oppressor.

All other tactical and ethical choices we make on social media regarding current events and general ethos usually stems from these two things.

So when it comes to current events (both the obvious ones, and ones that may come to be known in the future) I have two prime directives.

The first is that my core goal can and must be to destroy capitalism. Chancers are if you are following me at this point that's not something one would object to.

The second is, I oppose the oppressor whomever it is, always.

Whether it's the conflict in Israel/Palestine, the construction of Cop City, the ongoing trans genocide in the Imperial core, the calls for Landback and decolonization, or any other number of things; I will always oppose the oppressor.

All other tactical and ethical choices we make on social media regarding current events and general ethos usually stems from these two things.
